<strong>Swipely, recently named by&nbsp;</strong><strong>Providence Business News as one of the &quot;Best Places to Work in Rhode Island&quot; and by Forbes as &quot;One of America&#39;s Most Promising Companies&quot;,</strong><strong>&nbsp; is building an &ldquo;All-Star Team&rdquo; of highly motivated Account Executives(AE) to join our rapidly growing Providence, RI based inside sales team.</strong></p>
<p>
This is not your average inside sales job.&nbsp; AEs have fun while learning proven strategies from sales leaders who have built world-class local sales teams in the past.&nbsp; As an AE, you&#39;ll help transform how local merchants accept payments, understand customers and grow sales. Swipely&rsquo;s sales team has an inspiring energy and drive to win. We think big, we learn fast, and we get things done! If you&rsquo;re looking for an exciting&nbsp; career, great training and leading-edge tools to help you win, you&rsquo;ve come to the right place!<br />
