<strong>About Swipely</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
An award-winning place to work, named by <strong>Providence Business News</strong> as one of the <strong>&quot;Best Places to Work in Rhode Island&quot;</strong> and by <strong>Forbes </strong>as <strong>&quot;One of America&#39;s Most Promising Companies&quot;</strong></li>
<li>
The fastest-growing Silicon Valley-funded technology company in Rhode Island</li>
<li>
Founded, managed and backed by successful veterans of Microsoft, Google, eBay, LinkedIn, Facebook, Living Social and Seamless.com</li>
<li>
Disrupting a massive, growing $70 billion market for payments with innovation</li>
<li>
Helping hundreds of renowned local businesses better understand customers and grow sales while transforming the expense of accepting payments into a valuable marketing investment</li>
<li>
A fun and exciting start-up that empowers its people and offers growth potential</li>
</ul>
<p>
<br />
<strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Manage your own territory and drive the full sales cycle from introductory calls to online demonstrations to closing deals</li>
<li>
Educate prospective merchant members about Swipely&rsquo;s platform, knowing our product inside and out (we&rsquo;ll train you of course)</li>
<li>
Make a high volume of outbound sales calls to local business owners each day</li>
<li>
Meet and strive to exceed individual monthly sales goals</li>
<li>
Work closely with other teams to ensure smooth transition from initial contact to setting merchants live on the service</li>
</ul>
