Bachelor&rsquo;s degree and 1-3 years of sales experience (preferably selling to local businesses) required</li>
<li>
An entrepreneurial spirit: our AEs are hard working, well organized, self-motivated and confident</li>
<li>
A passion for sales, specifically technology that helps local merchants succeed</li>
<li>
Strong interpersonal skills: our AEs are energetic, outgoing, strong listeners, and able to balance confidence and resolve with humility and empathy</li>
<li>
A focus on constant improvement: our AEs embrace feedback and learn quickly. Swipely provides training and ongoing coaching to help you win and grow</li>
<li>
An advocate of using technology to succeed: our AEs use various tools to increase efficency including Salesforce.com extensively</li>
<li>
A fun loving team player who brings a positive attitude to the office everyday</li>
</ul>
